      "role": "user",
      "content": "i hear what you're saying about physics but it just feels so intentional. like why name it THAT if they're just \"coincidentally\" having signals hit certain rooms? and if they're smart enough to name it something that targeted, wouldn't they be smart enough to use something more subtle than just wifi signals to keep tabs on me? it feels like they're taunting me.",
